The first lesson I
learned was discipline,

01:09:06.280 --> 01:09:10.070
you will do as you're told.

01:09:10.070 --> 01:09:15.110
When you get off that bus

01:09:15.110 --> 01:09:26.900
on recruitment day you know
you're not in Kansas anymore.

01:09:26.900 --> 01:09:33.970
[Whistle sounds] Come on, let's
go, let's go, get on the line!

